{"tid":1042093,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【超雲29+1】IG公開真實年齡 何超蓮：畀我就寫少10年","createTime":"2019-03-01T10:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T15:27:02.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4540e9a3f32e8212321bdec3ef111a42d9e04a3f","tid":1042093,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:12:36.000Z","msg":"賭王千金何超蓮今天於中環出席化妝品牌活動，以全黑低胸性感打扮現身的她，自言是型格女人味，尤其喜歡所穿的黑絲。<br />\n提到家姐超雲昨天30歲生日，超蓮說：「係呀，好好笑，佢唔知喺邊度聽返嚟，話想要一隻紅雞蛋，不過媽咪唔識整，所以就咁烚咗一隻蛋畀佢。佢正常收到好多花，屋企成個花海咁。」超蓮指不清楚花束是否超雲的追求者所送：「咁靚女，追求者眾，應該有嘅。」她又指兩姊妹少有傾私人感情事，超蓮還大讚家姐主動在互聯網上寫上真實年齡，勇氣可嘉：「佢好有勇氣，喺ig寫30歲生日，畀我就寫少10年，19年開始有個10 years challenge，我post咗9歲時嘅相，好唔要面，我會周圍同人講19歲，睇吓大家信唔信。」<br />\n至於問到超雲的生日願望，超蓮透露說：「佢都係做嘢，同我一樣，大家都唔係向結婚方向行，佢比較低調，好深閨。佢文靜，我活潑，佢似媽咪，我似daddy。」超蓮又指超雲唔憂嫁：「緣份遇到就會遇到，佢唔憂趕住嫁，望落去得20歲頭，冇話29＋1就要結婚，呢個年代都遲婚。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190228/large/1551341825_5adf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190228%2Flarge%2F1551341825_5adf.jpg&h=3efc7d68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190228/large/1551341825_627f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190228%2Flarge%2F1551341825_627f.jpg&h=bee25b91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190228/large/1551341825_2543.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190228%2Flarge%2F1551341825_2543.jpg&h=c8acf20d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190228/large/1551341830_c538.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190228%2Flarge%2F1551341830_c538.jpg&h=c8b7d313&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190228/59314178\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190228%2F59314178&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7C5uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=a482c35f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190228%2F59314178&h=c233755b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190228/59314178</a>"},{"pid":"4d6ffdb32225d6628d4ef6ac3027111c49958a07","tid":1042093,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:14:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7925d6b2a8f352112524f49aff6b98c98afbf033","tid":1042093,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4d6ffdb32225d6628d4ef6ac3027111c49958a07","tid":1042093,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:14:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:14:17.000Z","msg":"求你比我埋佢單<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8506488fda3199690bf63ccb466385ed21578ac5","tid":1042093,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:14:41.000Z","msg":"咁撚有錢真係幫佢奶西奶埋屎眼都制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d429c40e53a1272083c0ee1d81153fc3b0c44da","tid":1042093,"uid":168911,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4d6ffdb32225d6628d4ef6ac3027111c49958a07","tid":1042093,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:14:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:15:02.000Z","msg":"超雲係中女啦，又未至於老態ge"},{"pid":"ac9da5fa535f2acfc39f84443b6126a280f5939e","tid":1042093,"uid":76098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:23:49.000Z","msg":"超雲好似靚左"},{"pid":"813d93f1322d14dc8011d45638491d93255ee49a","tid":1042093,"uid":154684,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0